snippet.title: [GOTY 2012 #1] Best VGM 1272 - Tribes Ascend - Temple Ruins
snippet.description:
Brute in a Tank video I made: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hsjRUADnTUo

Get Tribes Ascend for free: https://account.hirezstudios.com/tribesascend/?referral=1684013&utm_campaign=email

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC
Tribes Ascend (2012)
Temple Ruins
Chris Rickwood
